  "title": "Business Development Manager",
  "description": "<p><u><strong>Job Description</strong></u></p><ul><li>Planning and project management (PM) of data business related to insurance</li><li>Operation of existing data business</li><li>Promoting new data business - contacting clients, project management, new proposals etc</li><li>Strategic planning related to automobile insurance and other fields in Southeast Asia</li><li>Research, planning, and client approach for new businesses</li><li>Making presentation documents to report to Japanese HQ</li></ul><p></p><p><u><strong>Job Requirements</strong></u></p><ul><li>Over 7 years experience in insurance industry</li><li>Experienced in the operation and sales of insurance</li><li>Experience working with insurance related companies or insurance authorities</li><li>Business Level of Japanese language ability (equivalent to JLPT N1) is required for this position, as it involves frequent communication with our clients, other Japanese colleagues as well as our Japan Headquarter</li><li>Bachelor's degree in any discipline</li></ul>",
